'''Hypohidrosis''' is diminished sweating in response to appropriate stimuli. While [[hyperhidrosis]] is a socially troubling but [[benign]] condition, hypohidrosis can lead to [[hyperthermia]], heat exhaustion, heat stroke and potentially death.<ref name="AHYPO">{{Cite pmid|23094789|noedit}}</ref>

