===Medications===
* [[Anticholinergic agents]]
* [[Opioids]]
* [[Botulinum toxin]]
* Alpha-2 receptor antagonists
* [[Clonidine]]
* [[Barbiturates]]

===Physical agents===
* [[Tumours]]
* [[Burns]]
* [[Radiation]]
* [[Surgery]]
* [[Scars]]

